Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.51,0:02:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望煌珠與人類之間的戰爭能盡快結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.04,0:02:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由此而產生的一瞬間的彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.54,0:02:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使得蕾被ChaosChoir的幹部們帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.17,0:02:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下酷獨自消沉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「別失去戰鬥的氣力」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.73,0:02:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,清醒後發現周圍都是支持自己的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.27,0:02:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振奮精神後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.46,0:02:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷朝著漂浮在空中的決戰之地——煌珠樂園而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.69,0:02:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再過一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.39,0:02:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.23,0:02:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.91,0:02:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千鈞一髮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.66,0:03:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 好重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.59,0:03:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.44,0:03:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏就是煌珠樂園？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.63,0:03:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十四唱 煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.19,0:03:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼停戰的意向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.39,0:03:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必須盡快傳達給ChaosChoir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒準備好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.25,0:03:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.16,0:03:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克魯斯輔佐官的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「裝配推進力最強勁的」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.25,0:03:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼說不覺得太大了的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們覺得飛船會吃不消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但命令畢竟是命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.35,0:03:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祝你好運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像總算解決完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.63,0:04:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼的那幫人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多虧了有我們在 他們才能去避難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.51,0:04:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也暫時撤退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.07,0:04:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來不想輕易地放我們回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.68,0:04:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.19,0:04:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們煌珠的女王的王宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.72,0:05:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不希望有戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.81,0:05:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論是對人還是對煌珠來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要您來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.97,0:05:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 伊芙大人在等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊芙她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.64,0:05:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.01,0:05:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是伊芙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.98,0:05:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊芙大人 請寬心歇息去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.03,0:05:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊芙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.23,0:06:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個人也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直就像是廢墟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.78,0:06:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏真的就是煌珠樂園嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人的總部所在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.41,0:06:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是沒有留守兵力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.70,0:06:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是說下面的就是全部了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.54,0:06:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.55,0:06:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我們的城鎮沒什麼不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.68,0:07:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.89,0:07:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點找蕾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.80,0:07:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毀滅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.78,0:07:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女王是全體煌珠生命的源泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.99,0:07:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為伊芙大人的力量衰弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.86,0:07:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法孕育新的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.69,0:07:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在守護者體內嵌入人造核石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.33,0:07:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為我們的僕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才使我們得以生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這種破石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是那也已經到極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.11,0:07:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊芙大人離開了寶座的現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.66,0:07:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,置之不理的話煌珠樂園 孕育煌珠的這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.81,0:07:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會走上毀滅之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要拯救這一危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.53,0:07:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了新的女王登基之外別無他法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們尋找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.59,0:08:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 襲擊我們是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.99,0:08:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都是為了讓您坐上那個位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.92,0:08:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請救救我們 救救煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭將結束嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.31,0:08:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要我坐在那個位置上戰爭就將結束嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.25,0:08:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向您保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.71,0:09:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.89,0:09:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.91,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許是蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.61,0:09:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.45,0:09:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有看到過一個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她叫蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.92,0:10:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個子比你小 可愛或者該說是呆呆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說的話她也許會生氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.98,0:10:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能互相理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一方被消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.94,0:10:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知該怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和蕾在一起時這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是煌珠還是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要願意就能友好相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.53,0:10:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以別說那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.18,0:10:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.95,0:10:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.27,0:10:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.75,0:10:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.70,0:10:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 這裏...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.09,0:10:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 那不是蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.42,0:10:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才這裏有個煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.75,0:11:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭恭敬敬{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賀祝皇位繼承{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尊者無需開口{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玉裳加身{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祝頌七煌寶樹{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.55,0:11:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誠心誠意{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唱頌讚歌{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汝一代一代{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡皆賢明{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.93,0:11:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神秘之靈已成形{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.93,0:11:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親族之命不可違{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夜之繩索{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.61,0:11:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,索之在牢{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為天地{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受人膜拜{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來就是幹掉同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.97,0:11:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解除契約後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.74,0:11:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的女王就誕生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.82,0:11:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.43,0:11:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關鍵的同契者呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 什麼時候...
